\title{rcore: Templates and Utilities for nf-core Downstream Analysis and Visualization}
\description{
Provides a collection of R Markdown report templates, ggplot2 themes, colorblind-friendly colour palettes, and helper functions for downstream analysis of nf-core pipeline outputs. Supported workflows include RNA-seq, single-cell RNA-seq, ChIP-seq/ATAC-seq, spatial transcriptomics, methylation, and multi-omics. Templates are personalised at deploy-time using a user-level configuration so that any analyst or organisation can brand their own reports. Originally developed at the Harvard Chan Bioinformatics Core.
